{"tid":666500,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"［港匯］金管局出手買15.7億港元","createTime":"2018-05-16T02:26:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-16T08:10:10.000Z","uid":55257,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0b4c033a3da6aa3c4faa704aa191ac8b4c883a16","tid":666500,"uid":55257,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T02:26:39.000Z","msg":"港滙再觸及7.85弱方保證，金管局於紐約交易時段買入15.7億港元，令銀行體系結餘於本周四（5月17日）降至約1,269億港元。今次是金管局繼4月19日後再度入市，至今累計於市場共14度接錢，合共承接528.7億港元沽盤。<br />\n<br />\n港滙弱方兌換保證於4月12日倫敦交易時段首度觸發，其後隨著港元銀行同業拆息（HIBOR）上揚，港滙稍有回穩，自4月19日至4月底以來，弱方兌換保證沒有再被觸發。<br />\n<br />\n不過，自新股凍資潮過後，近日短期拆息回落，港美息差再次擴闊，港滙續於7.85邊緣徘徊，金管局再次入市。"},{"pid":"be00250a4c0a3701351f97cb92d1c81ca0846ea3","tid":666500,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"香港２０２０ 死!"},{"pid":"f8b0182856df75b95c4d4e934f18146e8a1e055e","tid":666500,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be00250a4c0a3701351f97cb92d1c81ca0846ea3","tid":666500,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"香港２０２０ 死!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"到時全世界都死<br />\n但&rdquo;樓市gogogo&rdquo; said by 業主s"},{"pid":"4a49858593d343714bd3448f1bf5717a90a960b3","tid":666500,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f8b0182856df75b95c4d4e934f18146e8a1e055e","tid":666500,"uid":129340,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be00250a4c0a3701351f97cb92d1c81ca0846ea3","tid":666500,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:01:58.000Z","msg":"香港２０２０ 死!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:21:36.000Z","msg":"到時全世界都死<br />\n但&rdquo;樓市gogogo&rdquo; said by 業主s"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:25:53.000Z","msg":"Ｆull pay果班唔死。。。。但上車果班，接樓，再買果班一定要死"},{"pid":"1444f9138528dcc98c3bb6ccc2751509c4431ac4","tid":666500,"uid":31773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-16T06:26:05.000Z","msg":"今次買少